  <li id="comment-12539" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/12198436879038391267" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Adrienne</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/11/out-of-love/#comment-12539"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-11-11T13:37:00-05:00">Tuesday, November 11, 2008 at 1:37 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh! Oh! I have a cabbage in my fridge! This is very exciting.</p>
