      <p>Molly&#8211;</></>Your recipe caused one of those lovely NYC moments. I went to my local cheeseshop and asked for the St. Marcellin&#8230; the woman behind the counter asked if I was making Molly Stevens recipe, then offered &#8220;I gave her the recipe&#8221;! We then proceeded to talk cheese, food and the like. </></>So if all goes according to plan, this recipe will yield three moments of loveliness&#8211;the happy accident of asking the right person for cheese, the delight of making the dish and, of course, the happiness of eating it.</p>
