    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>If you don&#8217;t have any good stock or broth on hand, let me recommend using half water and half white wine, with an extra dash of salt to make up for what you would have gotten from the broth. It doesn&#8217;t taste the same, of course, but it does taste good, and much better than tinny bad broth does.</p>
    </div>

