      <p>We enjoyed this for several days&#8230;so satisfying! I experimented with plain ole cabbage to see how it would work.  Trust me, just stick with the Savoy &#8212; the texture made a big difference, plus plain cabbage was too watery.  I&#39;ll bet Napa cabbage could work if you didn&#39;t use the watery core and spines.  I also experimented using white wine since I only had half a cup of ch. Stock in the freezer.  Not a good idea.  Thanks for the recipe!</p>
