      <p>Just made this (found your blog through a link when searching for savoy cabbage recipes, since I had 3/4 of a head leftover from some coleslaw I had made).  I don&#39;t even really like cabbage, but I cannot believe how wonderful this was; we had it with grilled pork chops.  Will definitely be making it again.</p>
    </div>

